        public TradeParty addGlobalId(ID additionalGlobalId)

        Adds the global vendor number or customer number ID.

        Example

        GLN, DUNS, BIC, ODETTE

        Example

        • ID.getValue() GENODED1SPK, 4000001000005

        • ID.getSchemeId() the ISO 6523 code 0021, 0088, 0060, 0177

        Parameters:
        additionalGlobalId - the additional global id
        Returns:
        the trade party
